      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   srt-pro-gia            .
           move      zero                 to   srt-pro-vgi            .
           move      zero                 to   srt-pro-gat            .
           move      zero                 to   srt-pro-vga            .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Coordinate riga documento               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bir-num-prt       to   srt-num-prt            .
