      *                      * Data documento relativa al tipo record  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-ofr-dat-doc       to   srt-dat-rec            .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Quantita' relativa al tipo record       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-ofr-qta-ord       to   srt-qta-rec            .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Quantita' da evadere                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test se la riga e' chiusa           *
      *                          * comunque                            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        rf-ofr-flg-rch       not  = spaces
                     move  zero           to   srt-qta-dev
                     go to stp-srt-inp-orf-620.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Test se la riga si considera evasa  *
      *                          * comunque                            *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        rf-ofr-sdr-ccs       not  = spaces
                     move  zero           to   srt-qta-dev
                     go to stp-srt-inp-orf-620.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Quantita' in ordine meno la quanti- *
      *                          * ta' gia ricevuta                    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      d-qev-rof-qta-ord    to   srt-qta-dev            .
           subtract  d-qev-rof-qta-ric    from srt-qta-dev            .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * In caso di super-evasione si pone a *
      *                          * zero la quantita' da evadere        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        srt-qta-dev          <    zero
                     move  zero           to   srt-qta-dev            .
