           move      "pgm/mag/prg/obj/pmag300y"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using d-sld-mag              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Giacenza di inizio anno                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      d-sld-mag-sld-mag    to   srt-pro-gia            .
       stp-srt-inp-gdm-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore relativo alla giacenza di inizio anno    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione con costo medio ponderato    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "VM"                 to   d-vun-mag-tip-ope      .
           move      0001                 to   d-vun-mag-tip-val      .
           move      w-stp-srt-inp-iar    to   d-vun-mag-dat-val      .
           move      01                   to   d-vun-mag-tip-mag      .
           move      rf-dcp-num-pro       to   d-vun-mag-num-mag      .
           move      "pgm/mag/prg/obj/pmag300v"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using d-vun-mag              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valore                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           multiply  srt-pro-gia          by   d-vun-mag-val-uni
                                        giving srt-pro-vgi            .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Applicazione decimali gestione magazzino    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           divide    100                  into srt-pro-vgi            .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Applicazione / 1000                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-arg-mag-ecu    =    "K"
                     divide  1000         into srt-pro-vgi            .
       stp-srt-inp-gdm-300.
