      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Ciclo Report Program : Esecuzione per fine ciclo          *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Stampa del file di riepilogo per le classi                *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       prn-fin-cic-frc-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di interruzione forzata    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-prn-flg-int      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se stampa da eseguire                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-tor-sta           not  = 03
                     go to prn-fin-cic-frc-900.
       prn-fin-cic-frc-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close file sequenziale-9 di appoggio            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cls-fil-sq9-000      thru cls-fil-sq9-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open input file sequenziale-9 di appoggio       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   opn-inp-sq9-000      thru opn-inp-sq9-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione contatore righe stampate        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-stp-fil-sq9-ctr      .
       prn-fin-cic-frc-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Reperimento record                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           read      sq9    at end
                            go to prn-fin-cic-frc-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Record letto in area di comodo                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      sq9-dat-rec          to   w-stp-fil-sq9-str      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento contatore righe stampate             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-stp-fil-sq9-ctr      .
       prn-fin-cic-frc-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se prima riga                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-fil-sq9-ctr    >    1
                     go to prn-fin-cic-frc-410.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Flag stampa sottolineature                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-stp-int-pag-ssf      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Intestazione pagina                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   int-pag-sta-000      thru int-pag-sta-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Flag stampa CGS                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-stp-int-pag-cgs      .
