           subtract  w-tot-sgr-bfo-vac    from w-det-mrg-lrd-vsc      .
           subtract  w-tot-sgr-pro-vgi    from w-det-mrg-lrd-vsc      .
           multiply  100                  by   w-det-mrg-lrd-vsc      .
           divide    w-tot-sgr-bol-vac    into w-det-mrg-lrd-vsc
                                        giving w-det-mrg-lrd-pmr
                                               rounded                .
